title: Presidential state car (United States)
summary: The United States presidential state car (nicknamed "the Beast",[1][2][3] "Cadillac One",[4][5] "First Car";[6] code named "Stagecoach"[7][8]) is the official state car of the president of the United States.  The current model of presidential state car is a unique Cadillac that debuted on September 24, 2018.
